      • search

        @GET
 @Path(value="search/{query}")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public javax.ws.rs.core.Response search(@PathParam(value="query")
                                                                                                                 java.lang.String input,
                                                                                                                 @QueryParam(value="type")
                                                                                                                 java.lang.String type,
                                                                                                                 @QueryParam(value="limit")
                                                                                                                 java.lang.String limit,
                                                                                                                 @QueryParam(value="offset")
                                                                                                                 java.lang.String offset)
        Rest API: Search. Currently Supports Title and People. Implementation performs partial word match provided word begins with the query. Support filtering by query param type
        Parameters:
        {query} - search query
        type - if type=person returns only people, if type=title returns only title. default if no type returns both
        limit - page size for pagination support. default is set at 100
        offset - offset for pagination support
        Returns:
